🔁 OR

❓ Write a trigger before insert record of customer. If the customer number is less than or equal to zero, then give the appropriate message.


---

✅ Trigger

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION check_cno()
RETURNS TRIGGER AS
$$
BEGIN
    IF NEW.cno <= 0 THEN
        RAISE EXCEPTION 'Invalid Customer Number';
    END IF;
    RETURN NEW;
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;

CREATE TRIGGER trg_customer
BEFORE INSERT ON customer
FOR EACH ROW
EXECUTE FUNCTION check_cno();


