🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept value of n and display sum of first n numbers.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE sum_n(n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    s INT := 0;
    i INT;
BEGIN
    FOR i IN 1..n LOOP
        s := s + i;
    END LOOP;

    RAISE NOTICE 'Sum = %', s;
END;
$$;


---

✅ Call

CALL sum_n(5);


